      "description": "KeyType dword 0x00 = DAK (AES-128) 0x01 = NMK (AES-128) 0x02 = NEK (AES-128) 0x03 = TEK (AES-128) 0x04 = Hash Key (Random-3072) 0x05 = Nonce Only (no key) 0x06-0xFF = Reserved"
